= Version 0.0.1
  * Imported from Rango
  * bin/simple-templater can generate a project or a stub
  * it can find all gems with simple-templater.scope file in the root
  * it has hooks running before & after templater
  * it knows how to work with diff stubs
  * it can have variables in file names of stub files
  * it can have collections in file names of stub files
  * it use Erubis for processing templates (all files ending with .rbt)
  * it has context and hooks for interaction with user (ARGV/STDIN)
